    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/7d529902d13f04c8ced9d61ed2bd2c8c.avif?t=1771332227\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras_big/7d529902d13f04c8ced9d61ed2bd2c8c.webp?t=1771332227 width=1560 height=197 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一款以中世纪中国为背景的第一人称城市建造游戏中，规划、建造并放松身心。你从一名朴实的工匠起步，循序渐进地规划、生产并筑起宏伟建筑。管理村民，搭建生产链，打磨物流，让你的村落以自己的节奏繁荣发展——无压力，并享受精巧系统带来的成就感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/a3857bf8852e2079f8d3b8626b96c17f.avif?t=1771332227\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras_big/a3857bf8852e2079f8d3b8626b96c17f.avif?t=1771332227 width=1560 height=578 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索三大区域——山间隘口、沙漠平原与肥沃河谷——各自拥有独特资源、挑战与令人忍不住截图的景致。地貌不仅是背景；它会塑造你的策略与可达成的目标。发掘古老工艺的秘密，精进手艺，建造传统中式地标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/815eb059b8347b2ed7f41d35d298c9e8.avif?t=1771332227\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras_big/815eb059b8347b2ed7f41d35d298c9e8.avif?t=1771332227 width=1560 height=322 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从切割石料、整形木材到烧制砖瓦、冶炼金属——每一座建筑都在清晰、合乎逻辑的阶段中成形。建起防御塔、荒漠要塞，以及传奇的箭扣长城“天梯”。你的工程同样推动聚落基础设施发展：作坊、窑炉、锻造坊与装饰工坊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/6ef6e3db907d85bbce6185833643b8e4.avif?t=1771332227\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras_big/6ef6e3db907d85bbce6185833643b8e4.avif?t=1771332227 width=1560 height=322 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你既是管理者，也是工匠。耕种田地、饲养牲畜、烹饪传统菜肴，并关照村民的福祉。自定义建筑、布置装饰，目送活力小镇逐步成形——非常适合安静的夜间时光。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/7ed920358f4e0b64ae73e80b91ff4be4.avif?t=1771332227\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras_big/7ed920358f4e0b64ae73e80b91ff4be4.avif?t=1771332227 width=1560 height=322 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着名望提升，赢得皇帝青睐，解锁新技法，精进本领，并以大师建造者之名载入史册。跟随匠师君（Jun）与其孙女梅（Mei）的故事，踏上一段关于技艺、传承与抱负的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>你会爱上《华夏山河》的理由</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深度建造与优化——清晰的生产链、合理的物流以及直接管理 NPC。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放松而不赶进度——按自己的节奏慢玩，享受项目完工的喜悦。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地道文化——取材于王朝中国的建筑、工艺与美食。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >引导性叙事——匠师主线为你的决策提供目标与背景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/e89efe22ca556eb5fc596c2735a350fc.poster.avif?t=1771332227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/e89efe22ca556eb5fc596c2735a350fc.webm?t=1771332227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/e89efe22ca556eb5fc596c2735a350fc.mp4?t=1771332227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真实、分阶段的建造机制（第一人称）与手工制作。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理工人、收集资源，并优化聚落内的生产流程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >三片广袤区域，各具资源、风险与建造技法。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造、制作、农耕、探索与装饰的多元融合。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正宗中式主题——从建筑到美食与室内陈设。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剧情驱动的战役与任务，引领你迈向建造世界奇迹之一。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/459ea0f598e289553f7be4090fa0a959.poster.avif?t=1771332227\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/459ea0f598e289553f7be4090fa0a959.webm?t=1771332227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1640820/extras/459ea0f598e289553f7be4090fa0a959.mp4?t=1771332227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>万里长城在等待着你。</strong><br><strong>在《华夏山河》中铸就你的传承。</strong></h2>",
